snippet.title: Turbo Tornado - Trailer
snippet.description:
Turbo Tornado: Open World Race is a breathtaking offline racing game designed for speed enthusiasts. In addition to the ever-expanding open world; Experience unique features such as vehicle customization, drift, night theme and police chases. Join us now and compete to become the king of the street!

Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Graypow.TurboTornado

App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/id6471108882
